Name: Average duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before any activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before transitioning to any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress' grouped by 'organization country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Median duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' across all variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in any case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' leading to a resolution ('Completed + Resolved' or 'Completed + Closed')
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases involving 'PROD582'

Name: Duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the variant with the highest performance
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases with high impact versus medium or low impact
